message: The name of Kosovo was changed, as there was never an official name (Kosovo and Metohija) used in the Constitutions of 1946, 1963 and 1974. It was called Autonomous Region of Kosovo in 1946 and 1963 and 1974 Autonomous Province of Kosovo. I also changed the year, as there is no serbian administration from 1999 on and from 2008 Kosovo is recognized from 116 countries as an independent country/nation. The flag was also wrong. It was the Albanian Eagle with a star.
